pageContent: Objective: To determine the clinical presentation and outcomes of prostate cancer in human immunodeficiency virus (HIV)-infected men compared with HIV-uninfected men in an urban setting.

metaData.source:
Investigating the role of psychological flexibility, masculine self-esteem and stoicism as predictors of psychological distress and quality of life in men living with prostate cancer
